\f1\b\fs34 \cf3 5. Opportunities for Differentiation
\f2\b0\fs28 \cf3 \
\
Given the features and competitors discussed, where can Mythos truly stand out? The goal is not just to be an amalgamation of Canva, HubSpot, Monday, and Zapier, but the 
\f3\b best possible version
\f2\b0  of such a platform. Here are key opportunities for Mythos to differentiate itself in the market:\
\pard\tqr\tx100\tx260\li260\fi-260\sl324\slmult1\sb240\partightenfactor0
\cf3 	\'95	
\f3\b \cf3 Seamless End-to-End Workflow
