\f2\i0 \cf3  tool a creator needs from content ideation to publishing. This unified approach is a major differentiator. Instead of hopping between five different apps, users stay in one environment. As Sprinklr\'92s editorial put it, the ideal is \'93finding the last content tool you\'92ll ever need\'94 . For individuals and small teams, Mythos can 
\f4\i \cf3 be
