	\'95	
\f3\b \cf3 AI at Every Step (Deep AI Integration)
\f2\b0 \cf3 : Many competitors add AI as an afterthought or a single feature (e.g., \'93generate caption\'94 button). Mythos can differentiate by making AI a pervasive, assistive presence throughout the platform:\
\pard\tqr\tx500\tx660\li660\fi-660\sl324\slmult1\sb240\partightenfactor0
\cf3 	\'95	AI suggestions in brainstorming (content ideas generator when calendar has gaps).\
	\'95	AI in creation (text, image, video generation as core features, not plugins).\
	\'95	AI in optimization (auto-enhance a design layout, rewrite text for a given tone with one toggle).\
	\'95	AI in scheduling (predictive performance, best-time auto scheduling).\
	\'95	AI in analytics (natural language reports: \'93Your LinkedIn posts grew 5% last week, primarily due to X\'94).\
	\'95	Perhaps even an 
\f3\b AI assistant chatbot
\f2\b0  within Mythos that understands the user\'92s content library and can answer or execute commands (\'93Mythos, draft a tech blog announcement and schedule it for next week across platforms\'94). In essence, Mythos could have a built-in \'93content concierge\'94 powered by AI \'96 a bold feature that few have attempted, and something that leverages the full-stack nature of the platform.\
\pard\tqr\tx100\tx260\li260\fi-260\sl324\slmult1\sb240\partightenfactor0
\cf3 	\'95	
\f3\b \cf3 Creator-Centric Design and Pricing
\f2\b0 \cf3 : Established enterprise tools often ignore individual creators or very small businesses by pricing them out or being too complex. Meanwhile, entry-level tools lack advanced capabilities. Mythos can target this gap with a 
