\cf3 	\'95	e.g., TikTok (short video) \'96 helping generate ideas or scripts for TikToks, perhaps integrating with TikTok\'92s API (which fewer schedulers do due to limitations).\
	\'95	Pinterest (visual stories, idea pins).\
	\'95	Medium or Reddit for written content distribution.\
	\'95	Podcast platforms (maybe Mythos can publish an audio snippet to a podcast feed).\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li660\sl324\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Supporting a broader range of channels (even if through integrations) could attract creators who operate in those spaces. It signals Mythos is 
\f4\i comprehensive
\f2\i0 .\
\
In conclusion, 
\f3\b Mythos\'92s differentiation
